            <p>Multiplying the cost per entity by the number of organisations in scope estimates communications set-up costs of <b>£14.7 million</b> (2024 prices) in the low scenario, <b>£17.8 million</b> (2024 prices) in the best/ central scenario and <b>£21.0 million</b> (2024 prices) in the high scenario.</p>
